# NotesJava.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Must be root to execute the jdk*.rpm.bin file.

Must be root to rpm -i the jdk* file.

Add link "ln -s /usr/java/jdk1.3.1_02 /usr/java/jdk" to make path to the development kit more generic.

If you have something like:
"Font specified in font.properties not found [--symbol-medium-r-normal--*-%d-*-*-p-*-adobe-fontspecific]"
appear when you run a gui, go to "/usr/java/jdk/jre/lib/font.properties" and comment out the lines that have references to adobe fonts.
Getting abode fonts may be an option also.